    topic: "Endocrinology",
    subtopic: "Osteoporosis - pharmacological management",
    stem: `A 55-year-old woman comes to your clinic because she is concerned about developing osteoporosis after menopause. Which one of the following is correct regarding the prevention of osteoporosis?`,
