    stem: `A 65-year-old female presents with a Colles fracture of the right wrist. Further workup shows that she is osteoporotic. She has a history of breast cancer, for which she was successfully treated with mastectomy and radiotherapy. Which one of the following would be the most appropriate management of her osteoporosis after taking care of the fracture?`,
